  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GCR - Centre for Families and Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A holistic approach will be adopted, allowing GCR&#x2019;s team to be able to offer a range of legal and social services, supported with supplementary activities for families, children and unaccompanied minors. The centre will inform and assist children and their families with access to basic health and care services, access to education and the provision of legal counselling, and psychological support. The initiative will operate in close co-ordination with other agencies with the objective of identifying the most vulnerable cases.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to facilitate the protection of children, families and minors by ensuring their access and utilisation of all appropriate and available services within the current protection framework in a specialised Family and Child Centre in Athens.</narrative>
  </description>
